2.caption: 2012 NFL Pro Bowl
2.description: The 2012 Pro Bowl was the National Football League's all-star game for the 2011 season. It took place at 2:00 pm local time on Sunday, January 29, 2012 at Aloha Stadium in Honolulu, Hawaii. The AFC defeated the NFC, 59–41.
2.inspected:Announcers: Dan Hicks, Mike Mayock, Doug Flutie, Alex Flanagan and Randy Moss
2.inspected:Coin toss: MG Rodger Mathews, U.S. Army; LtGen Thomas L. Conant, U.S. Marines & Maj Gen Darryll Wong, USAF
2.inspected:Halftime show: "NFL Salute to Service" (tribute to U.S. Armed Forces)
